headline.main: Liberals Seeking a Comeback Take Aim at Their Own Party
headline.print_headline: Liberals Seeking a Comeback Take Aim at Their Own Party

lead_paragraph: Four days after Donald Trump's surprising White House victory, the liberal organization CREDO Action fired off a frantic warning to its 4.6 million anxious supporters.
